{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-20",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_20_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 20 - If They Hang You",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 3,
  "page_total": 7,
  "page_start_sec": 496.14,
  "page_end_sec": 739.68,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.648,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 496.14,
      "end": 498.76,
      "text": "She looked at him with horrified wide eyes and cried,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 499.57,
      "end": 500.02,
      "text": "\"'Don't!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 500.02,
      "end": 501.42,
      "text": "Don't talk to me like that,"
    },
    {
      "start": 501.54,
      "end": 501.76,
      "text": "Sam!"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.02,
      "end": 503.36,
      "text": "You know I didn't!"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.4,
      "end": 504.48,
      "text": "You know!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 504.82,
      "end": 505.54,
      "text": "\"'Stop it!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.26,
      "end": 507.64,
      "text": "He looked at the watch on his wrist.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 508.2,
      "end": 509.92,
      "text": "\"'The police will be blowing in any minute now,"
    },
    {
      "start": 510.06,
      "end": 511.3,
      "text": "and we're sitting on dynamite."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.5,
      "end": 512.0,
      "text": "Talk!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.38,
      "end": 515.5,
      "text": "She put the back of a hand to her forehead.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 516.12,
      "end": 516.64,
      "text": "\"'Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.64,
      "end": 518.98,
      "text": "why do you accuse me of such a terrible—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 519.776,
      "end": 520.88,
      "text": "\"'Will you stop it?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 521.52,
      "end": 522.62,
      "text": "he demanded in a low,"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.74,
      "end": 523.52,
      "text": "impatient voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 523.8,
      "end": 526.46,
      "text": "This isn't the spot for schoolgirl manners."
    },
    {
      "start": 526.97,
      "end": 527.86,
      "text": "Listen to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.08,
      "end": 529.6,
      "text": "The pair of us are sitting under"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.6,
      "end": 532.44,
      "text": "the gallows.' He took hold of her wrists and"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.44,
      "end": 534.12,
      "text": "made her stand up straight in front of him."
    },
    {
      "start": 534.84,
      "end": 535.14,
      "text": "Talk.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 538.52,
      "end": 539.74,
      "text": "\"'I—I—how did you know",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 540.58,
      "end": 542.35,
      "text": "he—he licked his lips and looked?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 543.2,
      "end": 544.62,
      "text": "Spade laughed harshly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 544.74,
      "end": 546.02,
      "text": "\"'I knew Miles,"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.2,
      "end": 547.34,
      "text": "but never mind that."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.18,
      "end": 549.14,
      "text": "Why did you shoot him?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 549.16,
      "end": 549.18,
      "text": "him."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.14,
      "end": 553.46,
      "text": "She twisted her wrists out of Spade's fingers and put her hands up",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 553.46,
      "end": 554.54,
      "text": "around the back of his neck,"
    },
    {
      "start": 554.66,
      "end": 557.02,
      "text": "pulling his head down until his mouth all"
    },
    {
      "start": 557.12,
      "end": 557.86,
      "text": "but touched hers."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.92,
      "end": 561.58,
      "text": "Her body was flat against his from knees to chest.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 561.88,
      "end": 561.98,
      "text": "He"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.52,
      "end": 563.52,
      "text": "put his arms around her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.62,
      "end": 564.8,
      "text": "holding her tight to him."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.3,
      "end": 566.78,
      "text": "Her dark-lashed lids"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.78,
      "end": 568.82,
      "text": "were half down over velvety-blue eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 569.5,
      "end": 570.68,
      "text": "Her voice was hushed,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 570.7,
      "end": 571.26,
      "text": "throaty."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.02,
      "end": 573.14,
      "text": "I didn't mean to,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 573.3,
      "end": 573.88,
      "text": "at first."
    },
    {
      "start": 574.62,
      "end": 575.32,
      "text": "I didn't really.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 576.16,
      "end": 577.94,
      "text": "I meant what I told you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 577.98,
      "end": 580.64,
      "text": "but when I saw Floyd couldn't be frightened,"
    },
    {
      "start": 580.84,
      "end": 581.62,
      "text": "I—"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.112,
      "end": 583.28,
      "text": "Spade shook her roughly."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.58,
      "end": 584.22,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.832,
      "end": 585.38,
      "text": "That's a lie."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.66,
      "end": 588.0,
      "text": "You asked Miles and me to handle it ourselves."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.18,
      "end": 589.6,
      "text": "You wanted",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 589.6,
      "end": 592.6,
      "text": "to be sure the shadower was somebody you knew and who knew you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.74,
      "end": 593.18,
      "text": "so"
    },
    {
      "start": 593.34,
      "end": 594.06,
      "text": "they'd go with you."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.86,
      "end": 596.48,
      "text": "You got the gun from Thursby that day,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 596.66,
      "end": 597.4,
      "text": "that night."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.08,
      "end": 600.36,
      "text": "You had already rented the apartment at the Coronet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 601.22,
      "end": 601.44,
      "text": "You had",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 601.56,
      "end": 603.2,
      "text": "trunks there and none at the hotel,"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.46,
      "end": 606.36,
      "text": "and when I looked the apartment over I found a rent receipt"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.54,
      "end": 610.016,
      "text": "dated five or six days before the time you told me you had moved in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 611.46,
      "end": 612.66,
      "text": "She swallowed with difficulty",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 612.94,
      "end": 614.04,
      "text": "and her voice was humble."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.6,
      "end": 615.62,
      "text": "\"'Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 615.7,
      "end": 616.46,
      "text": "that's a lie,"
    },
    {
      "start": 616.58,
      "end": 616.78,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.02,
      "end": 618.36,
      "text": "I did mean to,"
    },
    {
      "start": 618.54,
      "end": 622.08,
      "text": "if Floyd—I—I can't look at"
    },
    {
      "start": 622.08,
      "end": 622.9,
      "text": "you and tell you this,"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.0,
      "end": 623.45,
      "text": "Sam.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.56,
      "end": 625.9,
      "text": "She pulled his head farther down",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 625.9,
      "end": 627.62,
      "text": "until her cheek was against his cheek,"
    },
    {
      "start": 627.82,
      "end": 629.32,
      "text": "her mouth by his ear,"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.44,
      "end": 630.18,
      "text": "and whispered,"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.24,
      "end": 633.2,
      "text": "\"'I knew Floyd wouldn't be easily frightened,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 633.36,
      "end": 635.92,
      "text": "but I thought that if he knew somebody was"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.0,
      "end": 636.54,
      "text": "shadowing him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.68,
      "end": 637.62,
      "text": "either he'd—'"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.04,
      "end": 638.46,
      "text": "\"'Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.58,
      "end": 639.5,
      "text": "I can't say it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.58,
      "end": 640.12,
      "text": "Sam!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.78,
      "end": 641.54,
      "text": "She clung to him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 641.56,
      "end": 641.96,
      "text": "sobbing."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.168,
      "end": 643.68,
      "text": "Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 644.58,
      "end": 646.0,
      "text": "\"'You thought Floyd would tackle him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 646.46,
      "end": 647.94,
      "text": "and one or the other would be killed."
    },
    {
      "start": 648.74,
      "end": 649.2,
      "text": "If Thursby",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 649.2,
      "end": 649.7,
      "text": "was the one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 649.82,
      "end": 650.94,
      "text": "then you were rid of him."
    },
    {
      "start": 651.6,
      "end": 652.22,
      "text": "If Miles was,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 652.46,
      "end": 653.78,
      "text": "then you could see that Thursby"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.9,
      "end": 656.8,
      "text": "was caught if he didn't go away then and you'd be through with him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 657.02,
      "end": 657.88,
      "text": "that it?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 658.976,
      "end": 659.94,
      "text": "\"'Something like that.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 660.64,
      "end": 663.36,
      "text": "\"'And when you found that Thursby didn't mean to tackle him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 663.46,
      "end": 664.82,
      "text": "you borrowed the gun from him"
    },
    {
      "start": 664.82,
      "end": 665.54,
      "text": "and did it yourself,"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.88,
      "end": 666.38,
      "text": "right?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.98,
      "end": 668.1,
      "text": "\"'Yes.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.08,
      "end": 671.84,
      "text": "\"'And then you thought Thursby would be nailed for the killing?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 672.5,
      "end": 672.98,
      "text": "\"'Yes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 673.06,
      "end": 674.76,
      "text": "And they'd hold him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.82,
      "end": 676.48,
      "text": "at least till after Jacoby had come,"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.6,
      "end": 677.62,
      "text": "and I'd had a chance"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.62,
      "end": 678.55,
      "text": "to get the Falcon.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.51,
      "end": 683.4,
      "text": "and you didn't know then you didn't even suspect that gutman was",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 683.4,
      "end": 686.46,
      "text": "here hunting for you or you wouldn't have wanted to shake your gunman"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.84,
      "end": 689.82,
      "text": "you knew gutman was here when you learned thursby had been shot"
    },
    {
      "start": 690.62,
      "end": 691.92,
      "text": "then you knew you needed another",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 691.92,
      "end": 693.98,
      "text": "protector so you came back to me right"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.78,
      "end": 694.88,
      "text": "\"'Yes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 695.72,
      "end": 695.872,
      "text": "But,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 696.36,
      "end": 696.88,
      "text": "oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 697.0,
      "end": 697.88,
      "text": "sweetheart,"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.44,
      "end": 699.42,
      "text": "it wasn't only that."
    },
    {
      "start": 699.68,
      "end": 702.04,
      "text": "I would have come back to you sooner or later."
    },
    {
      "start": 702.78,
      "end": 705.504,
      "text": "From the first instant I saw you I knew.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 706.4,
      "end": 707.58,
      "text": "Spade said tenderly,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 708.288,
      "end": 708.96,
      "text": "\"'You're an angel.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 709.2,
      "end": 709.3,
      "text": "Well,"
    },
    {
      "start": 710.04,
      "end": 711.24,
      "text": "if you get a good break,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 711.44,
      "end": 713.5,
      "text": "you'll be out of San Quentin in twenty years,"
    },
    {
      "start": 713.64,
      "end": 715.3,
      "text": "and you can come back to me then.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.44,
      "end": 717.8,
      "text": "She took her cheek away from his,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 718.14,
      "end": 720.88,
      "text": "drawing her head far back to stare up at him without comprehension."
    },
    {
      "start": 721.65,
      "end": 723.06,
      "text": "He was pale.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 723.32,
      "end": 724.68,
      "text": "He said tenderly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.72,
      "end": 727.74,
      "text": "\"'I hope to—they don't hang you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 727.76,
      "end": 728.08,
      "text": "precious,"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.22,
      "end": 729.632,
      "text": "by that sweet neck.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.04,
      "end": 732.58,
      "text": "He slid his hands up to caress her throat."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.88,
      "end": 735.74,
      "text": "In an instant she was out of his arms,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 735.84,
      "end": 736.92,
      "text": "back against the table,"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.06,
      "end": 737.66,
      "text": "crouching,"
    },
    {
      "start": 737.7,
      "end": 738.96,
      "text": "both hands spread"
    },
    {
      "start": 738.96,
      "end": 739.68,
      "text": "over her throat."
    }
  ]
}